{"tid":16172,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"網民 PS 改圖製作《水滸傳》108 條好漢歐美演員版本，形神兼備引起網路瘋傳","createTime":"2016-12-01T10:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T06:11:45.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7dab300bdf326fe3f519a693ee6e97d51a10a0","tid":16172,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"Hugh Jackman 版托塔天王<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/weibops1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fweibops1.jpg&h=017eb255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《水滸傳》為中國四大名著之一，其內容講述北宋梁山泊以宋江為首的 108 條綠林好漢，由被迫落草，發展壯大，直至受到朝廷招安，東征西討的歷程。就算沒有看過原作，其名稱也為人熟知，一直以來也有被拍成不少相關劇集 / 電影，那如果換成是在歐美拍攝會怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n微博網民@青紅造了個白就用 PS 製作了一個「歐美版水滸傳」，人物素材來自 2011 年的同名電視劇《水滸傳》，由於改圖效果非常好（而且很好笑），在網上非常受歡迎。大家可以看看以下的「演員列表」，陣容浩大 (如果真的找齊 108 人就太困難了)：<br />\n<br />\nDenzel Washington、Christian Bale 和 Benedict Cumberbatch<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/weibops2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fweibops2.jpg&h=8ff1b5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更多請轉至/ 轉貼自: <a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/176959/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-ps-%E6%94%B9%E5%9C%96%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%8A%E6%B0%B4%E6%BB%B8%E5%82%B3%E3%80%8B108-%E6%A2%9D%E5%A5%BD%E6%BC%A2%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2F176959%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-ps-%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%259C%2596%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25BB%25B8%25E5%2582%25B3%25E3%2580%258B108-%25E6%25A2%259D%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2589%2588%25E6%259C%25AC%25EF%25BC%258C&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f736bb71\" target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/176959/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-ps-%E6%94%B9%E5%9C%96%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%8A%E6%B0%B4%E6%BB%B8%E5%82%B3%E3%80%8B108-%E6%A2%9D%E5%A5%BD%E6%BC%A2%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n太多貼唔哂<br />\n請移玉步入去慢慢睇<br />\n多謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9258dc21d20733e75d5a46bc59ee39af73c66b","tid":16172,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/weibops11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fweibops11.jpg&h=61b4bc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f94c5b0262729a6abc6f3842fb5ee804f3e0f9","tid":16172,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eef18fe042bf1f30140797929dc9aa1a9150010","tid":16172,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}